name: El Rey del Mundo (Non Cuban) - El Rey del Mundo by AJ - Limited Edition Toro
brand: El Rey del Mundo (Non Cuban), El Rey del Mundo by AJ
additionalNotes: This full-strength toro delivers noticeable notes of earth, spice and sweetness. Its savory, dark Nicaraguan Habano wrapper covers a USA Connecticut Broadleaf binder and a Nicaraguan Habano filler. Developed by cigar impresario AJ Fernandez, this potent blend is perfect for seasoned aficionados or novices who want to expand their smoking portfolio. Once rolled, each cigar is draped with a soft tissue to protect its exquisite wrapper. The El Rey del Mundo by AJ Fernandez Limited Edition is handmade in Nicaragua.
